description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'The Full Pyramid | 30 Minute HIIT Indoor Cycling Workout' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.

Original workout description: Pyramid set of one-minute intervals increasing from 1/10 to 10/10 then back down to 1/10. Manon is joined by Nathan, Katie, Maddie and Morgan for this HIIT indoor bike workout. Get your water and towel readyâ€¦ Let's go!
